# Formspree Configuration
# To enable live email submissions:
# 1. Sign up at https://formspree.io/
# 2. Create a form and get your Form ID (e.g., abc123def456)
# 3. Replace the value below with your actual Form ID
# 4. In your Formspree dashboard, set up an email reply to:
#    - To: {Email}
#    - Subject: Enigmo Labs | Protocol Initialized
#    - Body: Hello {Name},\n\nYour brief has been received. Our lead architect, Ian Assah, will reach out via the phone number provided or this email within 12 hours.\n\nThe Future is Engineered.
#
# Leave as YOUR_FORM_ID to simulate submission (no emails sent) for development/testing.

VITE_FORMSPREE_FORM_ID=xvzllegn